<p rend="chapter">Paṭilomayamakagāthā</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="99"><hi rend="paranum">99</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Lokāyātatayā kālo visesaṃ na na saṃsevi,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Visesaṃ na na saṃsevi lokā yātatayā kālo.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="100"><hi rend="paranum">100</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Rājarājayasopetavisesaṃ racitaṃ mayā,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Yāmataṃ cirasaṃsevitapeso yajarājarā.</p>
